libfolia
------------------------------------------
This is a C++ Library, developed by Ko van der Sloot, for working with the
Format for Linguistic Annotation (FoLiA). The software is intended for C++
developers, and provides a high-level API to read, manipulate, and create
FoLiA documents. This software is a necessary dependency for various other
tools that use FoLiA.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.5-1
  libfolia-devel-2.21.1-1bl2
  libfolia22-2.21.1-1bl2
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libicu76-76.1-2
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  libticcutils10-0.36-1bl2
  libxml2-2.10.4-2
  libxml2-devel-2.10.4-2
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-2
  autoconf-archive-2024.10.16-1
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.45.1-1
  cygport-0.37.4-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  libicu-devel-76.1-2
  libticcutils-devel-0.36-1bl2
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  libxml2-devel-2.10.4-2
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/LanguageMachines/libfolia

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/LanguageMachines/libfolia/archive/refs/tags/v2.21.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libfolia-2.21.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libfolia-2.21.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libfolia-2.21.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libfolia-2.21.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libfolia22-2.21.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libfolia-devel-2.21.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libfolia)
  /usr/bin/foliadiff.sh
  /usr/bin/folialint.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libfolia.README
  /usr/share/doc/libfolia/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libfolia/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libfolia/MAINTAINERS
  /usr/share/doc/libfolia/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/libfolia/README
  /usr/share/doc/libfolia/TODO
  /usr/share/man/man1/folialint.1.gz

(libfolia22)
  /usr/bin/cygfolia-22.dll

(libfolia-devel)
  /usr/include/libfolia/folia.h
  /usr/include/libfolia/folia_document.h
  /usr/include/libfolia/folia_engine.h
  /usr/include/libfolia/folia_impl.h
  /usr/include/libfolia/folia_metadata.h
  /usr/include/libfolia/folia_properties.h
  /usr/include/libfolia/folia_provenance.h
  /usr/include/libfolia/folia_subclasses.h
  /usr/include/libfolia/folia_textpolicy.h
  /usr/include/libfolia/folia_types.h
  /usr/include/libfolia/folia_utils.h
  /usr/lib/libfolia.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/folia.pc

